@persistent-inlet, thanks for sharing your concern—it's completely understandable to feel anxious about posting online. We do want everyone to feel safe and comfortable sharing here.

If you ever have doubts about whether something might be flagged, you can always review the FAQ (link in the sidebar or profile) or message me directly and I can help clarify the rules. We're here to help and make sure the space stays positive for everyone.

And @braised-centroid, I'm glad you agree—being informed definitely helps. Let's all do our part to keep the forum welcoming and respectful.
